<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06128j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06128j">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06128j"> 128(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> loved the hero when saw less house</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Arch&eacute;g&egrave;te, id&eacute;al que l&apos;homme de g&eacute;nie incarne en ses chefs-d&apos;oeuvre, j&apos;aime mieux &ecirc;tre le dernier dans ta maison que le premier ailleurs. Oui, je m&apos;attacherai au stylobate de ton temple; j&apos;oublierai toute discipline hormis la tienne, je me ferai stylite sur tes colonnes, ma cellule sera sur ton architrave. Chose plus difficile! pour toi, je me ferai, si je peux, intol&eacute;rant, partial. Je n&apos;aimerai que toi. <br><font color="green">[Archegetes, ideal that the man of genius incarnates in his masterpieces, I&apos;d rather be the last in your house than the first one elsewhere. Yes, I will attach myself to the stylobate of your temple; I will forget all discipline except I will make myself stylite on your columns, my cell will be on your architrave. More difficult thing! for you, I will, if I can, intolerant, biased. I will only love you.]</font> <small> Ernest Renan, <a name="ERSD" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ERSD"><cite title="source">Souvenirs d'enfance et de jeunesse</cite></a> (1883) ?69</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c01180j" href="c01all.htm#c01180j">VI.C.01:180(j)</a></mm></dd> </dd></dl>
